rom\": 301, \"to\": 308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shortly after the disappointing outcome, Alonso announced her retirement from the sport to her 600k followers onInstagram.\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the disappointing outcome\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 350}, {\"ngram\": \"Alonso\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 358}, {\"ngram\": \"her retirement\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 398}, {\"ngram\": \"her 600k followers\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Swimming: thank you for allowing me to dream, you taught me to fight, to try, perseverance, sacrifice, discipline and many more,' Alonso said.\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alonso\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics 'I gave you part of my life and I do not change it for anything in the world because I lived the best experiences of my life, you gave me thousands of joys, friends from other countries that I will always carry them in my heart, unique opportunities.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 651}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 679}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"the best experiences\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 765}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"joys\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"other countries\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"unique opportunities\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 901}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's not goodbye, it's see you soon.'\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alonso has since been the subject of headlines after theParaguayan Olympic team said she had been removed from the athletes' village just a few days before the closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alonso\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"the subject\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"headlines\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 991}, {\"ngram\": \"theParaguayan Olympic team\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1024}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Her presence is creating an inappropriate atmosphere within Team Paraguay,' said Larissa Schaerer, the head of the COP mission.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1190, \"end\": 1198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\": 0.9645497300296668, \"rank\": 0.03675317438547448, \"text\": \"Paraguay\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}, {\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larissa_Schaerer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larissa Schaerer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larissa_Schaerer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larissa_Schaerer\"}, {\"begin\": 1240, \"end\": 1243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conference_of_the_parties\", \"score\": 0.9995304618218811, \"rank\": 0.0002644663984403718, \"text\": \"COP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conference_of_the_parties\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conference_of_the_parties\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her presence\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"an inappropriate atmosphere\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"the head\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We thank her for proceeding as instructed, as it was of her own free will that she did not spend the night in the athletes' village.'\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"proceeding\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1282}, {\"ngram\": \"her own free will\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1328}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Responding to claims she created an 'inappropriate atmosphere', Alonso said: 'I just wanted to clarify that I was never kicked out or expelled from anywhere, please stop spreading false information.\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"claims\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"an 'inappropriate atmosphere\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"Alonso\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"false information\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not want to make any statement but I am not going to let lies affect me either.'\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any statement\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"lies\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alonso, who was born in Asuncion, made her Olympic debut at the last Games but also failed to challenge for a medal in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1702, \"end\": 1710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asuncion_Island\", \"score\": 0.9901457869990256, \"rank\": 0.00994492078330046, \"text\": \"Asuncion\", \"types\": [\